node.text: #AD For my birthday this year, I planned a small get together with friends. If you know me then you know when I plan an event, I’m all about giving my guest “an experience.” With @chapstick Party Packs, I did just that! Party Packs give you 10 party-ready designs with delicious flavor options for each celebration type. Grab a “Happy Birthday” in Birthday Cake, “It’s a Baby” in Angel Food, or “Toast to Love” in Vanilla Kiss. If you’re planning a unique event, then go to ChapStick’s website to customize your party pack for a party favor that expands the joy of these moments that matter. #CelebratewithChapStick
